OL,12,     GBlues - Mayfair's most famous
OL,13,     Gstripper. She must use her
OL,14,     Gpleasing assets to defuse the
OL,15,     Gongoing criminal activity,
OL,16,     Gsurrounding the nightclub she
OL,17,     Gperforms in.
